      • coalesceTraversals

        public <V> V coalesceTraversals(java.util.concurrent.Callable<V> callable)
                         throws java.lang.reflect.InvocationTargetException
        Description copied from interface: IPatternMatcherRuntimeContext
        The given runnable will be executed, and all model traversals will be delayed until the execution is done. If there are any outstanding information to be read from the model, a single coalesced model traversal will initialize the caches and deliver the notifications.
